snippet.textDisplay:
Allahu Akbar Lyrics
Ya kareem’o ya gaffar’o raheem’o
Azeemo saari urr raza
Uspe hi raazi rahun
Jo kiya tune mujhko ata

Yeh jo nagamat ki mala hai
Mere gale mein padi

Tasbih isko bana de ilaahi x (2)

Allahuma itni asaluka birehmatika ya zul-jalal
Apne kiye pe jhukaye hu sar main ranj-o-malal

Tu jo sune na sunaunga kisko
Ye fariyad main

Tu hi sami ul basi ul mujib x (3)

Rabbe azaan ilaahi bhi tu
Marham bhi tu aur jalaali bhi tu
Khulfa ya kulga bhi khaalid hai tu

Tu rabbe mustafa, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe murtaza, Allahu Akbar
Rabbe sirate mustakeem, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe kaaba, Allahu Akbar
Nooh ki kashti ko dekhta hoon
Mauze nedamat mein dooba hua hun

Ya rahim, karde tu mujhko gurbat ataa
Ya rahim, kar guzar karde meri khata
Ya karim, rehmat ka teri talabgar hun
Ya rahim, banda main tera gunehgar hun

Dariya-e-atish mein hum
Bas yoon hi jal jayenge
Kar do sahara ab ne
Ya rab sambhal jayenge

Tu hi to woh roshni hai ke jis’se
Main gafil hua
Jaane anjane gunahon se kuchh bhi
Na hasil hua

Ho teri nazrein karam to
Yeh mushkil tal jayegi
Tu hi latiful khameerul hanif
Ho tu hi latiful khameerul hanif

Rabbe deewar-e zulkarnain tu
Rabbe mehraj-e kaunain tu
Rabbe ismail-o zamzam bhi tu

Tu rabbe ibrahim, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe jibrail, Allahu Akbar
Rabbe malaika, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe kausar, Allahu Akbar

Apne gulamo ki be-gulami
Ya mutakabir ya malik ya maghni

Ho roze hashr ka andaza nahi
Bakhshish ka samaan laya nahi
Hai meri ilteja
Kar de gurbat ata
Kar de reham o karam
Muskin hai tere dar pe khada

Mere iraade jo tute to
Mujhko pata yeh chala
Teri huqumat mein hoga wohi
Bas jo tune kaha

Apne habib ke sadke mein
Sunle meri yeh dua
Ho tu hi muqid ul hasib ul jalil

Rabbe zarde haidar hamza bhi tu
Rabbe asaaye musa bhi tu
Tu ru-ba-ru bhi aur hai ku-ba-ku

Tu rabbe eesa, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe mariam, Allahu Akbar
Rabbe sahaba, Allahu Akbar
Tu rabbe panchta, Allahu Akbar

Nooh ki qashti ko dekhta hu
Mauje nidamat mein dooba hua hu

Ya rahim, ya karim
Ya rahim, ya karim

Ya rahim, karde tu mujhko gurbat ataa
Ya rahim, kar guzar karde meri khata
Ya karim, rehmat ka teri talabgar hun
Ya rahim, banda main tera gunehgar hun
